Title: Various Checks for Citrix XenApp 7.x Farms
Level: 1
Component: checks
Compatible: compat
Version: 1.2.7i3
Date: 1435942897
Class: feature

Several new checks to gather information on Citrix VMs, hostsystems and controllers.
<tt>citrix_state</tt> monitors various state variables of citrix instances, such as
the power or registration state. <tt>citrix_controller</tt> checks whether the controller
is active or not, <tt>citrix_controller.licensing</tt> monitors the licensing state,
<tt>citrix_controller.session</tt> checks for the number of total, active and inactive
sessions. Also included are a number of purely informative checks that are always OK.
